{"tid":2189891,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"郭嘉文生日甫靚相被惡意攻擊 被鬧扮上流：你和梁洛施差太遠","createTime":"2020-09-05T08:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T12:05:14.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d1fecf19c568a117bfec545971f7d02937f394da","tid":2189891,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:10:40.000Z","msg":"「小小超」李澤楷女友、2015年港姐季軍郭嘉文（Karmen），日前度過28歲生日，人緣唔錯嘅佢連開幾個慶生Post，同3名大學女友人喺酒店房舉行派對，床上放滿氣球，非常夢幻。之後又同圈中好姊妹林凱恩食飯慶祝，呢個生日似乎過得好精彩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2740000/2744499/118394502_359007858436051_6809883880940085547_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2740000%2F2744499%2F118394502_359007858436051_6809883880940085547_n_600.jpg&h=cd1ec51b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b44fdf070896016d178826fc18526a7983bdfe6","tid":2189891,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:10:52.000Z","msg":"郭嘉文於社交平台大曬靚相，身穿吊帶衫輕露事業線，露出燦爛笑容，留言：「這一年算是很正式的辦了場生日會，有親親為我布置，感覺被寵，多謝美美老闆娘的蛋糕，今年仲可以同公主噹噹（狗狗）慶祝添。朋友聚在一起就是會互相說笑，說起大學時期的趣事&hellip;&hellip;因為妳們，今年的生日絕對難忘。」"},{"pid":"97ff2fdfe4df3402ba0756eeebe12120aefcdd91","tid":2189891,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2740000/2744499/118509646_1656387961182772_3871552119800850726_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2740000%2F2744499%2F118509646_1656387961182772_3871552119800850726_n_600.jpg&h=1b858bb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"295cf9b5def2952f238cd8e4c40bb031439dfe81","tid":2189891,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"唔少人都留言祝福佢，仲話好羨慕佢同大學同學嘅感情可以Keep到依家，叫佢好好珍惜咁真摯嘅友誼！不過有人祝福嘅同時都有「酸葡萄」惡意攻擊，仲拎為李澤楷生咗3個小朋友嘅梁洛施同佢比較，仲不停咁人身攻擊，幾難聽都有！"},{"pid":"b168272d0a36109d795768e8d773d284a38ce3c2","tid":2189891,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2740000/2744499/005ZDc0rgy1gg23wepogqj329k29kx6p_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2740000%2F2744499%2F005ZDc0rgy1gg23wepogqj329k29kx6p_600.jpg&h=dc31b71b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1661e28d9354d74ab2fa1ec50e89e1c88dbaa212","tid":2189891,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:11:46.000Z","msg":"幸好都有唔少網民好理智，話睇完佢打一大段真係黑人問號，話呢個口出惡言嘅網民只係出於妒忌。唔少人都大讚梁洛施同郭嘉文各有美態，梁洛施有一種令人驚艷嘅感覺，而郭嘉文乖乖女嘅外形亦非常順眼，百看不厭。"},{"pid":"0d9092e739c87784ad6400a1e3b177dea835577d","tid":2189891,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2740000/2744499/118600850_3380672458637429_8090977470070812729_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2740000%2F2744499%2F118600850_3380672458637429_8090977470070812729_n_600.jpg&h=ef04181d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac021acddb542192b6606ca68498ce4b8f6c2361","tid":2189891,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:12:11.000Z","msg":"郭嘉文與李澤楷拍拖4年，她一直低調處理感情事，甚得男友歡心，李澤楷亦一改以往低調處理感情事嘅習慣，在多次被目擊同Karmen去多國遊玩後，問到兩人感情事？他首度回應：「We are fine, thank you.（我們很好，謝謝。）」去年4月尾，李澤楷仲首度同Karmen一齊現身馬場活動，確認女友地位。"},{"pid":"461a3625898d1a8eb85cdca6a550728881481051","tid":2189891,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2740000/2744499/dc5049ebd0f5a35122569876fa7eb34d_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-s